This is a hosties based map. posted below is what it currently has in it.

1. 6 cells
2. 4 teleporters going to last request spots.
3. 2 teleporters going to secret room.
4. 2 watch towers.
5. 2 one-way glass walls.
6. Last Request spots
    1.GunToss/JumpShot
    2.Race
    3.Chicken/KnifeFight
    4.Shot for Shot aka Long shot

Please pm with any bug and or request. If you would like to edit this map in anyway please message me with what you would like to edit. also keep my name in credits.
